  "detailed_description": "In this tactical shooter you lead a special police task force. Your missions include counter-terrorism, hostage rescue, and targeting organized crime.<br><br>Use your voice to issue commands to your squad or to hostages. Order you team to clear rooms or provide cover for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447210/extras/6444a765de9886180543d27555608fe0.poster.avif?t=1604305720\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447210/extras/6444a765de9886180543d27555608fe0.webm?t=1604305720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447210/extras/6444a765de9886180543d27555608fe0.mp4?t=1604305720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose from a wide variety of weapons like rifles, electric tasers, knives, sledge hammers, or grenades. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447210/extras/755ec0a0107989c3db0928066d47cf23.poster.avif?t=1604305720\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447210/extras/755ec0a0107989c3db0928066d47cf23.webm?t=1604305720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447210/extras/755ec0a0107989c3db0928066d47cf23.mp4?t=1604305720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Internet connection for Voice Recognition is required.<br>The game is fully playable without Voice Recognition.",
